60.name: Buy mixed salad

Spend two wooden chips to buy a mixed salad (+1.50M health when eaten), filled with five types of fruit and lettuce!
To keep competition fair, you're not allowed to resell this food

61.name: Buy packed meal
61.tooltip:
Spend five wooden chips to buy a packed meal (+2.50M health when eaten), contains all major food groups!
To keep competition fair, you're not allowed to resell this food

62.name: Gather steel
62.tooltip:
Shovel molten steel right out of the furnace! There must be a safer way to obtain this...
Every completion causes 1.00 M damage, reduces all active food cooldowns by 10% of your maximum cooldown, and provides 1 steel per completion (Used for construction)

Provides 1 portion of honey per completion (+1.1M health when eaten)
